wikipedia_page.main: Michael John Murphy (born 5 May 1977) is an English former professional footballer who played in the Football League and National Conference League as a Striker, before moving to play in Scandinavia in the Finnish Veikkausliiga and Ykkonen league as a left sided midfielder and wing-back. Finishing his career in semi-professional football in the United Kingdom
